{"title":"诗人纳兰性德逝世三百周年纪念","authors":["蔡若虹"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":7,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗人纳兰性德逝世三百周年纪念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蔡若虹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侧帽难遮薄宦名，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一生憔悴伴啼莺；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱轮碾碎梨花梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衙鼓敲残野鹤情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道德归真观胆略，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才华出众听心声；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫愁冷暖无人识，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万古诗盟胜酒盟。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}